http://allafrica.com/stories/201505211008.html?viewall=1
[The General Auditing Commission (GAC) defends accounting irregularities during Ebola emergency.]

21 May 2015 Russia to donate USD 2 million to UNICEF in Ebola fight
http://www.africabusinesscommunities.com/news/west-africa-russia-to-donate-$2m-to-unicef-in-ebola-fight.html
[According to an agreement signed Wednesday night [20 May 2015] in New York, Russia will allocate USD 2 million to the United Nations Children's Fund programs to fight Ebola in Guinea, Liberia and Sierra Leone.]

22 May 2015 UN: USD 88.1 million needed for "last mile" of Ebola response -- United Nations official
http://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/more-news/183475-88-1m-needed-%E2%80%8B-for-%E2%80%8Blast-mile-of-%E2%80%8Bebola-%E2%80%8Bresponse-un-official.html

